parameter.help:
Yes or No. Yes enables client cookies. Default is Yes. If you set this attribute to 
		"No", Railo does not automatically send the CFID and CFTOKEN cookies to the client browser;
		you must manually code CFID and CFTOKEN on the URL for every page that uses Session or Client variables.

Title for collection;
Query column name for type and a valid query name;
Permits searching collections by title or displaying a separate title from the key
